    "long_instructions": "# Behavior-Based Anomaly Detection  \r\n\r\nThis chatbot has been fine-tuned to provide insights into **Behavior-Based Anomaly Detection** and its role in cybersecurity.  \r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n### Explore AI in Security (Activity)\r\n- Interact with the chatbot to understand how **Behavior-Based Anomaly Detection** works and how it helps prevent cyber threats.  \r\n- Use the **Conversation Starters** below to guide your exploration:  \r\n   - **Solution Overview:** *How does Behavior-Based Anomaly Detection work?*  \r\n   - **Problem Addressed:** *What network vulnerabilities does it target?*  \r\n   - **Pros & Cons:** *What are the advantages and limitations of this solution?*  \r\n   - **Project Application:** *How could this be used to mitigate risks in my chosen company scenario?*  \r\n\r\n### Risk Assessment Application \r\n- Use the chatbot’s responses to refine your **Network Security Risk Assessment** by identifying how Behavior-Based Anomaly Detection could help **identify, track, and respond** to suspicious activity before an attack occurs.  \r\n\r\n### **Tip:**  \r\n- If the chatbot’s response is unclear, try **rephrasing your question** with more details for a **more targeted answer**.  \r\n",
